# Uber Data Analysis

This project looks at Uber ride data to understand patterns like when people travel, how far they go, and how usage changes over time.

---

## What I did

* Cleaned and explored the dataset
* Converted date/time data for analysis
* Analyzed ride patterns (time, distance, frequency)
* Visualized trends using graphs

---

## Dataset

Contains ride-level details such as:

* Start and end time
* Pickup and drop locations
* Distance (miles)
* Purpose of trip

---

## Approach

Focused on exploratory data analysis (EDA) to find trends like:

* Peak booking times
* Most common trip purposes
* Distance distribution

---

## Key takeaway

Ride data can reveal clear usage patterns like busy hours and common trip types, which can help in better planning and decision-making.

